        <h2 id="how-thestacc-helps">How theStacc helps</h2>
        <p>theStacc pulls GBP Insights into a monthly local SEO report — queries, actions, seasonality, and post-level impact — alongside your rank-tracking and website analytics. The result: one dashboard that connects "which query triggered the listing" to "which action followed" to "which website page closed the loop". Insights becomes a decision-making tool, not a monthly screenshot.</p>

